briefdescription.para: The class Remeshing_triangulation_3 is a class template which provides a valid triangulation type that can be used as the 3D triangulation input for the tetrahedral remeshing process.

parameterdescription.para: is the geometric traits class. It has to be a model of the concept RemeshingTriangulationTraits_3.
enables sequential versus parallel implementation of the triangulation data structure. Possible values are Sequential_tag (the default), Parallel_tag, and Parallel_if_available_tag.
must be a model of RemeshingVertexBase_3.
